r than it amplifies the plane\rquote s violent characteristics. Players are encouraged to come up with their own implementations, though each }{\i\f30\fs20 exalted}{\f30\fs20  site should only have one enhanced feature and shouldn\rquote 
t provide more than a minor bonus, if any.
\par 
